  Keh ni5 te7-ji7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 “Lan5-hiong” chhut-si3, sim chin ai3 cha-pou--e5, na7-si7 iu5-goan5 seN cha-bou2--e5, m7-ku2 chit-e5 gin2-na2 chhut-si3 seN-chiaN5 kap lang5 bo5 siang5, phiN7, bak8, chhui3 chin sui2, phiN7 koan5 koh chiam, bak8-chiu toa7 lui2 koh teng5-sun5, chhui3 se3-e5, chhui3-tun5 chin poh8-tiah, hiN7-a2 tong5-ng-tui3, chhui3 e7-tau2 hui5-hui5, chin-chiaN3 u7 ho2 mia7-siong3 e5 khoan2-sit. Sou2-i2 Eng2-hok so2-ah khoaN3 liau2 chin hoaN-hi2. A-ma2 khoaN3 liau2 chhio3 bi-bi. Chit-e5 cho7 kap lau7-pe7 siang7-seN3, chiu7 kio3 i choe3 “Li2 Lan5-hiong”, chiu7-si7 lan2 sou2 kong2, choe3 goa7-kho e5 hou7-su7 pan-tiuN2 e5 “Lan5-hiong-che2”. Lan5-hiong Sio2-chia2 si3-hoe3 hit ni5, in lau7-bu2 koh khioh chit8 e5 sio2-moai7, ka7 i mia5 kio3 “Lan5-ji5”. Na7-si7 bo5 phah-sng3 chin put-heng7, Eng2-hok-so2 ti7 goeh8-lai7 28 jit8 chiu7 li7-khui se3-kan. ThiaN kong2 hit-e5 goan5-in chiu7-si7 in-ui7 ti7 soaN-lai7, bo5 gau5 e5 san2-po5, na7 u7, si7 eng7 thou2 khioh-chia2-ma2. Teh khioh e5 si5, kio3 i lang5 loh8-lai5 bin5-chhng5-kha, eng7 ke7 i2-thau5-a2 tian-to3-peng2 khng3, lang5 chiah che7 tiam3 i2-a2-kha e5 teng2-bin7, be7 su na2 teh heng5-hoat8, chit8 pian3 koh chit8 pian3, khah theng5 kio3 i khi2--lai5, pak-tou2 na7 thiaN3, chiu7 kio3 i koh loh8-khi3 che7, an2-ni chhia-poah8-peng2; kau3 eN-a2 chhut-si3 e5 si5, eN-a2 chin toa7-han3, ia7 be7-hiau2 eng7 chhiu2 khi3 sin5, ka7 i po2-hou7, kan-ta theng3 i chu7-jian5; seN liau2-au7 lang5 chin loan2-jiok8, ia7 be7-hiau2 eng7 sim2-mih8 khah ho2 e5 chiau3-kou3; au7-lai5 thiaN kong2 si7 thai-i bo5 chiau5 chhut--lai5, khioh-chia2-ma2 ia7 m7-chai. 
  Lang5 kong2 ui na7 chhut--lai5, tioh8 iuN2-chui2 lai5, eng7 ui khng3 ti7 chui2-te2 lai5 siong5-se3 kiam2-cha, khoaN3 u7 chiau5 chhut--lai5 a2-bo5? Na7 u7 khih-kak, a2-si7 koh-iuN7, tek-khak tioh8 chhiaN2 hu7-kho e5 i-seng lai5 chin2-chhat. Bo5, chhin3-chhin3 chhai2-chhai2 pau-pau khi3 hiat-kak8, au7-lai5 tiau5 ti7 lai7-bin7 e5 kiaN-lang5 hoat-chhau3 u7 tok8, tui3 an2-ni chiN-koaN5, chiN-jiat8, ia7 be7-hiau2 kin2 khi3 jip8-iN7, sim2-mih8 kong2 si7 leng2-tioh8, kin2 koan3 kiuN-bo2-te5, kong2 beh hou7 i hoat-kam2, sit8-chai7 chin kai-si2. Thai2 e7 thai-i bo5 chiau5 chhut--lai5, goan5-in kong2 si7 khioh-chia2-ma2 beh tian2 chhiu2-toaN7, kong2 tioh8 ai3 kin2 liah8-ui, ui kau3 u7 chit8 e5 si5-kan, i chu7-jian5 e7 pak-li7 chu2-kiong, na7 kau3 si5-kan koe3 siuN-ku2 khiok u7 gui5-hiam2, chong2-si7 m7-thang siuN-kin2 ka7 i nge7 khiu2. Chit pai2 chiu7-si7 nge7 khiu2, sou2-i2 u7 tiau5 chit8 sio2 pou7-hun7 ti7 lai7-bin7, chiah e7 ti3-kau3 gou7 tioh8 seN3-mia7. 
  Ah! Sit8-chai7 chin kho2-lin5, chiah-nih chiaN5-mih8 e5 chi2-moai7 kap tiong7-hu khiN5-khiN5 khip8-khip8, kan-kan khou2-khou2 lai5 khiN5-ke, jiat8-sim sin3 Chu2, hu-chhiong3 hu7-sui5, chit8 e5 bi2-boan2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 ka-teng5, an2-ni ui7-tioh8 bo5 i-hak8-siong7 e5 siong5-sek, m7-tioh8 e5 chhu2-ti3 lai5 sit-loh8 chit8 e5 lang5. Hit ni5 Eng2-hok-hiaN tu2-chiah 30 hoe3, Eng2-hok-so2 tu2-a2 chiah 29 hoe3, sit8-chai7 chin kho2-lin5, pang3 3 e5 kiaN2, chit8 e5 7 hoe3, chit8 e5 4 hoe3, chit8 e5 tu2 chhut-si3. Tong-si5 Lan5-hiong sio2-chia2 chiu7-si7 tu2 4 hoe3. Eng2-hok-so2 si2-loh8, chit8 ke soaN3 phun2-phun2, kai-chai3 lau7 tiuN7-m2-a2 iau2 chin khong-kian7 thang ka7 i tau3 io hiah-e5 gin2-na2, u7 khah-tit tiap8-ah. Na7 bo5 sit8-chai7 chham2 bo5 lang5 chai. 
  ThiaN-kiN3 Eng2-hok-so2 Chhiu-kui3-ah beh tng7-khui3 e5 si5, tui3 Eng2-hok-ah e5 chhiu2 giu2 tiau5-tiau5, hian2-beng5 hit-e5 saN-thiaN3 e5 tiN-bit8 m7-kam pun-khui, chiah choe3 ang-bou2 thau5-boe2 9 ni5 si7 8 ni5 chiok, pang3 3 e5 se3-kiaN2, chit8 e5 chiah toa7, chit8 e5 hiah toa7, bok8-koai3 sim kan-khou2. Na7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 be7 thang i5-ek8, bok8-su-niu5 kap chhu3-piN e5 chi2-moai7 tai7-ke ti7 chhng5-cheng5 bo5 m7 long2 lau5 bak8-sai2. A-thiam-m2 ia7 siuN7-khi2 A-thiam-peh e5 su7, chiu7 kim3 be7 tiau5 chau2-khi3 chau3-kha chhngh-chhngh hau2. Kau3 hit mng2 pou oa2 4 tiam2 lian5, Eng2-hok-so2 chiu7 an-jian5 to3-khi3. Keh jit8 chhut-chong3, thong kau3-hoe7 bo5 m7 ui7-tioh8 i lau5 bak8-sai2. Eng2-hok-hiaN chhu2-au7 ka-chai3 bo5 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni lai5 loe2-chi3, leng2-sim. Iu5-goan5 ke3-siok8 jiat8-sim hok8-sai7 Chu2, i e5 tiuN7-m2 kin-ni5 sui-jian5 si7 60 goa7 hoe3, soaN-nih lang5 sin-the2 iau2-ku2 chin iong2, chin gau5 thiaN3 hiah-e5 sun-a2, sou2-i2 put-chi2 choe3 Eng2-hok-hiaN e5 pang-chan7. ThiaN-kiN3 Eng2-hok-so2 Chhiu-kui3-ah beh tng7-khui3 e5 si5, kau-tai3 kui2-na7-ku3 oe7, chiu7-si7 kong2, tioh8 the3 i sioh hiah-e5 kiaN2, kap iu2-hau3 lau7-bu2, koh tioh8 jiat8-sim khiN5-tiau5 ti7 Chu2, Chu2 tek-khak beh si-un. Hit-si5 Eng2-hok-ah bak8-sai2 si3-lam5-sui5, ku3-ku3 ka7 i in3 ho2, tim3-thau5 lai5 an-ui3 i, au7-lai5 Eng2-hok-so2 e5 bin7 tng2-chhio3, kong2, “Chu2 lai5 lah, Chu2 lai5 lah, tai7-ke chhiaN2 !” Kong2 soah chu7 an2-ni koe3 khui3. 
  Sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni, m7-ku2 be7 bian2-tit u7 jin5-cheng5 e5 iu-bun7. Cheng5 na7 chhut-mng5, gin2-na2 kau-tai3 lau7-bu2 io, chit8 tui3 hu-hu7 koe-leh8-a2 ti3-teh, chit8 e5 giah8 ti-thau5, chit8 e5 taN pun3-ki, tang5-chhut tang5-jip8, jit8-am3 chiah toa7-taN3 taN tng2-lai5, chhio3 gi7-gi7, hoaN-hoaN hi2-hi2, taN hut-jian5 piN3 choe3 thian-gai5 e5 kou-gan7, kou-toaN chit8 chiah sim iu-bun7. Kau3 hng5-nih, chhan5-nih, kau3 phiaN5-teng2 khoaN3 tioh8 eng2-koe3 choe3 hoe2 che7 e5 chioh8-thau5, choe3 hoe2 bih-ng2 chiah8 tiong-tau3 e5 png7-pau e5 sou2-chai7, put-ti put-kak bak8-sai2 tou lian3 chhut--lai5. U7 si5 khia7 teh, kha sng chhiu2 nng2, gang7-gang7 sin5-sin5, soa3 m7-chai beh an2-choaN2, u7 si5 thou2 toa7-khui3, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 khi3 bong7-nih hau2-hau2 leh, kam2-kak sim na2-chun2 khah khin-sang. In-ui7 bong7 si7 tai5 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 phiaN5 e5 piN-ah, chiu7-si7 cheng5 chho3 kam-chia3, i phah-si2 choa5 hiat khi3 e5 sou2-chai7; m7-chai kong2 bak8 chit8-nih, hit si5 chheng-lian5 sui2 e5 bin5-bang7 ia7 i2-keng chiaN5 choe3 koe3-khi3 lah. 
