  8. Poah-loh8 Cheng5-bang7
  Na7-si7 Eng2-hok-hiaN hui-siong5 pa-kiat, i koat-sim m7 koh chhoa7, an3-chiau3 i e5 keng-giam7, i kam2-kak tin5 chiap bih8 si7 khun3-lan5, pat8-lang5 e5 bo2 m7 aN5 pat8-lang5 e5 kiaN2. I na7 siuN7-tioh8 cha2 in lau7-bu2 koh ke3 e5 cheng5-heng5, i ti7 in au7-chek hia sou2 siu7-tioh8 cheng-sin5-tek e5 thong3-khou2, i chiu7 na2 koat-sim m7 koh chhoa7. Ki5-sit8 m7-si7 kong2 thong se3-kan au7-chek, au7-bo2 chiu7-si7 long2 phaiN2. Chin chhut-mia5 e5 Bi2-kok chong2-thong2 A-pek-liap8-han2 Lim5-kheng2 e5 au7-bo2, pi2 chhin-seN pe7 iau2 khah e7-hiau2 liau2-kai2 i. I ia7 it-seng iu2-hau3 i e5 au7-bo2, choe3 chong2-thong2 e5 si5, ia7 si7 bo5 pian3-oaN7 i e5 hau3-sim, bo2-kiaN2 ia7 si7 chin chhin-bit8. Lan2 Tai5-oan5 ti7 Ki-tok-hoa3 ka-teng5 tiong khoaN3-tioh8 hit khoan2 ho2 au7-chek, ho2 au7-bo2--e5 ia7 bo5 chio2. Na7-si7 Eng2-hok-hiaN ti7 se3-han3 kiaN liau2 jip8-sim, thou2-oe7 kong2, “KiaN phoa3-taN2 khi3 lah,” sou2-i2 lian5 kaN2 siuN7 tou m7-kaN2, lang5 tui3 teng2 po3 kau3 e7, i long2 si7 chhio3-chhio3 in3 lang5 kong2, “Chiah lai5 siuN7 khoaN3-mai7, hou7 lin2 chin to-sia7.” Bak8 chit8-nih koe3 5, 6 ni5, lang5 chiu7 chai i bo5 i3-su3 beh koh chhoa7, tai7-ke ia7 chin chun-keng3--i, in tiuN7-m2 khoaN3 i an2-ni ia7 chin kam2-sim. 
  Tui3 Eng2-hok-so2 koe3-sin sng3 khi2 tu2 10 ni5 e5 7 goeh8 poaN3, hit jit8 chin joah8, A-thiam-m2 ti7 chhu3-au7 hiahN chha5, m7-chai chaiN2-iuN7 sio koe7-kha soa3 poah8 loh8-khi3, thau5-khak siang3 tui3 chioh8-thau5 loh8-khi3, tai7-khai3 si7 nau2 chin2-tong7, a2-si7 nau2-kin tng7-khi3, in-ui7 i chin hoat-hok, peng5-si5 hiat-ap ia7 chin koan5, tiaN7 kio3 thau5-khak gong5, sou2-i2 hun7-khi3 chin ku2, kiu3 cheng-sin5 chhiaN2 i-seng lai5 khoaN3, sui-jian5 u7 chu3-sia7, chiah8 ioh8 long2 bo5 kong-hau7, lang5 bin5-bin5 bo5 siaN2 chai lang5, an2-ni u7 jit8-goa7 chiu7 lai5 li7-khui se3-kan. TaN chia m7-bian2 siong5-se3 kong2. Kong2 Eng2-hok-hiaN hit ni5 tu2 40 hoe3. TaN ka-chai3 toa7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lan5-eng ia7 17 hoe3 lah, tai7-khai3 ke-lai7 e5 su7 tou long2 e7-hiau2 choe3, sou2-i2 bo5 kam2-kak sim2-mih8 toa7 khun3-lan5. Te7-ji7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lan5-hiong 14 hoe3, tu2 pit-giap8 kok-bin5 hak8-hau7, chun2-pi7 beh kho2 chhou-tiong. Te7 saN cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lan5-ji5 11 hoe3, kok-bin5 hak8-hau7 saN lian5 thak8 liau2 beh koe3 si3-lian5. Chit8 ke ia7 si7 chin lau7-jiat8, Eng2-hok hiaN chin thiaN3 chiah-e5 kiaN2, chiah-e5 kiaN2 ia7 chin iu2-hau3. Toa7-che2 Lan5-eng teng2 in lau7-bu2 e5 khoeh, ia7 si7 chin oah8-tang7 gau5 pang-chan7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 kap gim5-si-pan. Eng2-hok-hiaN siuN7 kong2 ai3 kha-chhiu2, chiu7 ti7 keh ni5 Lan5-eng 18 hoe3 ni5-boe2, khoaN3 u7 tu2-ho2 siang7 kau3-hoe7 e5 chheng-lian5, chiu7 ka7 i chio jip8--lai5. Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 e5 an-pai5, chin-chiaN3 tit-tioh8 chin ho2 e5 kiaN2-sai3. I ia7 chin kong-to7, chin-chiaN3 si7 ho2 pa-pah. Chiu7-si7 chiong in tiuN7-lang5 cha2 e5 giap8, long2 teng-ki3 hou7 in toa7 cha-bou2-kiaN2, phin2 na7 seN toa7 sun, tioh8 koh thng5 chit8 e5 seN3 Bok8. Tui3 an2-ni kiaN2-sai3 ia7 chin kam2-sim in tiuN7-lang5 e5 ho2-i3, chin iu2-hau3 khiN5 ke. Chiah-e5 tai7-chi3 an3-ha7 bian2 kong2. 
  Si5-jit8 teh koe3 chin kin2, lai5 kong2 Lan5-hiong sio2-chia2 bian2 goa7 ku2 chhou-tiong chiu7 pit-giap8. Pun2 siuN7 beh koh thak8 ko-tiong, na7-si7 in lau7-pe7 kong2 ai3 i oh8 sim2-mih8 ki-ge7 khah ho2. I ka-ki7 siuN7 in lau7-bu2 e5 si2, chiu7-si7 in-ui7 bo5 i-hak8 siong5-sek, sou2-i2 i chiu7 kap lau7-pe7 chham-siong5 khi3 kho2 hou7-seng. Chin u7 chai5-tiau7, chit8 pian3 chiu7 kho2-tioh8. M7-na7 an2-ni, i ti7 lan2 e5 peN7-iN7 hok8-bu7 4 ni5 au7, u7 khi3 hou7 cheng3-hu2 kiam2-teng7 san2-po5, chit8 pai2 chiu7 thong-koe3, au7-lai5 ke3-siok8 koh ti7 piN7-iN7 choe3 hou7-su7. Sou2-i2 lan2 e5 peN7-iN7 chin tiong7-iong7 i. An2-ni chiah e7 jim7 i choe3 goa7-kho e5 hou7-su7 chu2-jim7. 
